node.text:
It's very grand...

{{emote|*She shines a light from her laser pistol upward, craning her neck to look at the ceiling. *}}

It seems like a place of worship. These vaulted ceilings, the pillars carved with inscryptions. Maybe an ossuary and gold stockpile, if we're lucky. You ever take a trophy, =name=?

{{emote|She sizes up your intimidating posture...}}

Fifty fifty, then. Let's go, tomb-seeker. I'll be right behind you.

If you find the door, tell me. I'm not giving up this key, but I'll unlock the way forward for us.
